					<p> For an ACP exporter of fruit and vegetables, it is not always easy to find relevant documentation on European sanitary quality and traceability requirements. To help ACP companies improve their quality management and have access to up-to-date information, PIP has just launched this toolbox, a virtual library on CD that will solve the problem of access to information by minimizing the Internet connection difficulties that often complicate information search in ACP States.</p>
