					<p> Mon, 23 May 2005 | This reports explores agricultural research systems in Africa and assesses the need for further capacity building in this area. This needs assessment is conducted with a particular focus on the role that NEPAD should play in that context. The report argues that capacity building to enhance agricultural science in Africa is an area to which NEPAD should give high priority.</p>
