<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Selected-publications/Eight-case-studies-on-seed-aid-in-Africa" title="Eight case studies on seed aid in Africa" alt="link">Eight case studies on seed aid in Africa</a></h2>

	
					<p> Mon, 23 May 2005 | This volume contains eight case studies on seed aid in Africa. The case studies were undertaken to evaluate various forms of emergency seed aid in the field and to couple these with analyses of the broader seed and crop systems. The objectives were to understand if and how vulnerable farmers are being helped by the kinds of assistance they receive - and how to move forward on improving practice.</p>
							<p><span class="date">7/06/2005</span></p>
